data.description: Welcome to this original midcentury pool home. Currently set as a 3 bedroom, but can be easily be turned into a 4 bedroom home plus a den. If you love that cool mid century vibe, then move in and enjoy it! Or renovate this spacious home to your taste. Large interior laundry room. Cozy den with great view of the pool has a half bath with an extra washer that could be turned into a third full bath. One car carport with attached utility shed for storage or workshop.  Double gate on side yard for safe parking of your boat, equipment trailer or RV. Nice quiet neighborhood with nearby park and boat launch.
